14
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:33,800
Guo De-you found out that he is the Holy Child

15
00:00:33,950 --> 00:00:35,340
and decided to part ways with Gu Ying.

16
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:38,370
Heartbroken and dispirited, Gu Ying drank poison.

17
00:00:38,540 --> 00:00:41,570
Lian Hua-qing brought the Junior Tientsin Mystic to the abandoned factory again.

18
00:00:41,700 --> 00:00:44,070
They reached the underground cave via a hidden passageway.

19
00:00:44,260 --> 00:00:46,430
