Ding Mao and Father Xiao's relationship broke down.

21
00:00:48,270 --> 00:00:50,170
Xiao Lan-lan left along with Ding Mao.

22
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:52,340
Ding Mao worshipped the deceased sages at the Chamber of Commerce，

23
00:00:52,490 --> 00:00:54,640
then led the gang to the factory

24
00:00:54,810 --> 00:00:56,440
to fight with members of the Demonic Cult.

25
00:00:56,590 --> 00:00:59,790
In the middle of the fight, the factory chimney blew up with a great bang.

26
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:02,360
Grievances precede the plan's execution.

27
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,950
Carnal punishment precedes the scheme's success.

28
00:01:04,150 --> 00:01:06,280
The hero beats his chest and the beauty weeps tears of blood.

29
00:01:06,410 --> 00:01:10,280
From that moment on, the Tientsin Mystic exists no more.

30
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:16,320
Do you still dare to beat others up?

31
00:01:17,130 --> 00:01:19,550
They deserved it for saying that I don't have a father.

32
00:01:20,970 --> 00:01:23,690
Master, why can't I call you father?

33
00:01:23,980 --> 00:01:26,470
The one who births and raises you is your father.

34
00:01:27,660 --> 00:01:29,450
I only raised you.

35
00:01:29,750 --> 00:01:32,110
I cannot have you call me father.

36
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:35,370
A teacher for a day is a father for a lifetime.

37
00:01:35,570 --> 00:01:37,000
It's only an appellation.

38
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,700
We shouldn't concern ourselves over it.

39
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,820
How many are left?

40
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,630
Two.

41
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:46,810
How many?

42
00:01:47,770 --> 00:01:48,840
Three.

43
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:03,680
Someone once told me,

44
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,720
and I have always remembered it,

45
00:04:07,010 --> 00:04:09,880
that one cannot stop a river from flowing into the sea.

46
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:13,730
It's now time for this river to flow into the sea.

47
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:16,339
Even if it doesn't make a big splash,

48
00:04:16,589 --> 00:04:18,320
at least I have rushed through this journey

49
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:19,390
without looking back.

50
00:04:20,390 --> 00:04:21,839
At least it will be more meaningful

51
00:04:22,110 --> 00:04:24,300
than flowing over stones and leaves

52
00:04:24,530 --> 00:04:26,040
in the woods.

53
00:04:27,310 --> 00:04:28,070
Haven't you always wanted to

54
00:04:28,410 --> 00:04:30,260
eradicate the Demonic Cult?

55
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:33,090
The Demonic Cult can be eradicated,

56
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,300
but the human heart can't be cleansed.

57
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,800
Xue Yuan-yuan

58
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:46,270
was killed by her own father Xue Qing-yang.

59
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,640
Her child

60
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:51,770
was thrown into the river by Ding Yi-qiu.

61
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:53,740
Ding Yi-qiu and Shopkeeper Wang

62
00:04:54,060 --> 00:04:55,710
