63
00:04:56,730 --> 00:04:59,640
Feng Er-ma was killed by one of his own, Sun Lao-qi.

64
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:01,820
Those who stormed the British Consulate

65
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,350
and killed the British counsul

66
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:06,200
were zombies created by Mrs. Hu.

67
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:08,720
Her own son

68
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:09,510
Hu Tian-ming was one of them.

69
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:11,570
As for Huang Yi-suo,

70
00:05:11,730 --> 00:05:13,100
he was killed by his younger brother Huang Yu.

71
00:05:13,930 --> 00:05:16,570
Miss Xiao's fiancé, Mr. Qian,

72
00:05:16,870 --> 00:05:18,530
and over 100 bodies in the Hai River,

73
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:21,540
were all killed by Ding Mao's father Ding Yi-qiu

74
00:05:21,690 --> 00:05:23,240
with opium.

75
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:27,430
The Demonic Cult are the true victims.

76
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:30,420
They are just a group of patients

77
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,250
who want to alleviate their own pain.

78
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,250
What's wrong about that?

79
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:37,800
The root of this pain,

80
00:05:38,770 --> 00:05:39,930
and the origin of the Demonic Cult

81
00:05:40,170 --> 00:05:41,150
are here.

82
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:10,760
Lan-lan! Lan-lan!

83
00:06:11,690 --> 00:06:12,690
Lan-lan!

84
00:06:23,230 --> 00:06:24,070
