I'm dying, Young Master.

86
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,000
I'm dying.

87
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:36,710
Stay still.

88
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,100
I am going to get help.

89
00:06:38,930 --> 00:06:40,400
Wake up, Lan-lan!

90
00:06:43,610 --> 00:06:45,430
Our brothers are all dead.

91
